A2.25 2.25 0 007.5 21h6a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25V15m3 0l3-3m0 0l-3-3m3 3H9\"></path></svg>Demo<svg class=\"w-3 h-3 ml-auto transition-transform duration-150 \" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M19 9l-7 7-7-7\"></path></svg></button></div><button class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-full py-1.5 text-gray-400 hover:text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:bg-[var(--color-primary)]/5 rounded-lg transition-all duration-150 group\" title=\"Collapse\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:-translate-x-0.5\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M15.75 19.5L8.25 12l7.5-7.5\"></path></svg></button></div></aside><div class=\"flex-1 flex flex-col min-w-0\"><div class=\"hidden lg:flex items-center h-12 px-6 bg-white border-b border-gray-200\"><nav class=\"flex items-center gap-2 flex-1\"><a class=\"text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md transition-colors text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/?type=buy\">Buy</a><a class=\"text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md transition-colors text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/?type=rent\">Rent</a><a class=\"text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md transition-colors text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/sell\">Sell</a><a class=\"text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md transition-colors text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/agent\">Manage Rentals</a><a class=\"text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md transition-colors text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/list-property\">Advertise</a><a class=\"text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md transition-colors text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md transition-colors text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a><a class=\"text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md transition-colors text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/help\">Get Help</a></nav><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><a class=\"text-xs text-white bg-[var(--color-primary)] px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md hover:bg-[var(--color-primary-light)] transition-colors\" href=\"/login\">Sign In</a></div></div><main class=\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto pb-16 lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"flex-1\"><section class=\"bg-gray-50 py-16 px-4 border-b border-gray-200\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center\"><span class=\"text-xs font-medium text-[var(--color-primary)] uppercase tracking-wider\">Fair Housing</span><h1 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-2 mb-3\">Fair Housing Guide</h1><p class=\"text-gray-500 max-w-lg mx-auto\">MBPP is committed to equal housing opportunity for everyone in Kano State and across Nigeria.</p></div></section><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12\"><div class=\"prose prose-sm max-w-none text-gray-600 space-y-6\"><div class=\"bg-[var(--color-primary)]/5 rounded-lg border border-[var(--color-primary)]/10 p-6 text-center mb-8\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-primary)] flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3\"><span class=\"text-white font-bold text-lg\">EO</span></div><h2 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900\">Equal Housing Opportunity</h2><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1 max-w-xl mx-auto\">We do not discriminate on the basis of race, colour, religion, sex, disability, familial status, or national origin.</p></div><h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900\">Our Commitment</h2><p>MBPP is dedicated to providing equal housing opportunities to all individuals regardless of their background. We believe that everyone deserves a fair chance to find a home they love, and we hold our agents, ambassadors, and partners to the same standard.</p><p>Discrimination in housing is prohibited under the Constitution of the Federal Republic of Nigeria (1999) and relevant state laws. MBPP has a zero-tolerance policy for any form of housing discrimination on our platform.</p><h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900\">Protected Classes</h2><p>Housing discrimination includes denying housing, setting different terms, or providing unequal service based on:</p><ul class=\"list-disc pl-6 space-y-1\"><li>Race, colour, and ethnicity</li><li>Religion and belief</li><li>Sex, gender, and sexual orientation</li><li>Disability and health status</li><li>Family status and marital status</li><li>Age</li><li>National origin and place of birth</li></ul><h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900\">What We Do</h2><ul class=\"list-disc pl-6 space-y-1\"><li>All listings on MBPP are reviewed for discriminatory language or requirements</li><li>Agents and ambassadors undergo fair housing awareness training</li><li>Our platform features are accessible to users with disabilities</li><li>We provide translations and support for non-English-speaking users</li><li>We investigate all discrimination complaints promptly and thoroughly</li></ul><h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900\">Reporting Discrimination</h2><p>If you believe you have experienced housing discrimination through MBPP or any property listed on our platform, please report it immediately.</p><div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-5 mt-4\"><div class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\"><p><strong>Email:</strong> fairhousing@mbpp.ng</p><p><strong>Phone:</strong> +234 800 000 0000</p><p><strong>In Person:</strong> No. 15 Bompai Road, Kano Municipal, Kano State</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-8 p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\"><h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Fair Housing Resources</h2><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\"><li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:underline\">Nigeria Mortgage Refinance Company (NMRC) — Fair Lending Guidelines</a></li><li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:underline\">Federal Ministry of Works and Housing — Tenant Rights in Nigeria</a></li><li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:underline\">Kano State Urban Planning and Development Authority (KNUPDA)</a></li></ul></div></div></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main></div></div><nav class=\"lg:hidden fixed bottom-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 bg-white border-t border-gray-200 pb-safe\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-around h-14\"><a class=\"relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-0.5 h-full px-3 transition-colors duration-150 active:scale-95 text-gray-400\" href=\"/\"><svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M21 21l-5.197-5.197m0 0A7.5 7.5 0 105.196 5.196a7.5 7.5 0 0010.607 10.607z\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-[10px] font-medium \">Browse</span></a><a class=\"relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-0.5 h-full px-3 transition-colors duration-150 active:scale-95 text-gray-400\" href=\"/saved\"><svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M21 8.25c0-2.485-2.099-4.5-4.688-4.5-1.935 0-3.597 1.126-4.312 2.733-.715-1.607-2.377-2.733-4.313-2.733C5.1 3.75 3 5.765 3 8.25c0 7.22 9 12 9 12s9-4.78 9-12z\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-[10px] font-medium \">Saved</span></a><a class=\"relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-0.5 h-full px-3 transition-colors duration-150 active:scale-95 text-gray-400\" href=\"/messages\"><svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7.5 8.25h9m-9 3H12m-9.75 1.51c0 1.6 1.123 2.994 2.707 3.227 1.129.166 2.27.293 3.423.379.35.026.67.21.865.501L12